values: Yes today is Thursday. I hate today 'cause I hate Thursday's. But today is the day of silence which is pretty fun! I am not really looking foreward to the rest of the day, but more to the 4 day weekend starting tomorrow.
What is your biggest fear? Mine is a Subaru. They are everywhere. I cannot escape! The Outbacks are taking over.

Revalation! I feel really good today. I got all my homework done. Now I feel free. So, That is my entry. So long and thanks for all the fish!
